{"tid":776227,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[尖咀運氣強盛] 港鐵尖沙咀站炒扶手電梯 嚇到乘客分頭走","createTime":"2018-08-11T22:35:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T00:17:42.000Z","uid":80516,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a0e4d26006ab65c275c9fea624b79593523a8694","tid":776227,"uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T22:35:15.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=OPdEuTM8pvrXw7khawfK%2BGowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=63140328\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】港鐵尖沙咀站發生炒扶手電梯意外！今日(11日)傍晚6時許，站內一條由月台通往大堂的扶手電梯，於運行期間，梯頂突然發出「嘭」一聲巨響，隨即有零件四散，梯級變形，梯梳飛彈而出，至少6塊彈到梯頂地面，而電梯亦隨即停頓。當時電梯滿載乘客，紛紛嚇得急忙閃避，有人更高聲尖叫，在上段的乘客匆匆檻過變形損毀的梯級逃離，而在電梯中段至下段的乘客則趕忙掉頭向下走離開，在大堂的乘客則好奇圍觀已損毀的電梯，議論紛紛。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港鐵職員接報到場，封閉肇事扶手電梯，又用帆布遮蓋，同時通知承辦商派員到場維修。港鐵發言人回應指，事發時港鐵車站控制室職員發現有燈號着起，示意一條由月台上大堂的扶手電梯安全裝置啟動，扶手電梯停止運作。職員到場檢查後，發現扶手梯最上端梯級及梯梳損毀，扶手梯損壞原因有待調查，事件中沒有收到有人受傷報告。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/MFwHt1blOgSb3iMC.uitww--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/b61d5e2a701b91db87064192acb05305\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FMFwHt1blOgSb3iMC.uitww--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Fb61d5e2a701b91db87064192acb05305&h=99e01bc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/6yp_uPbTpt4HXrKyJGJDSw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/108735d7b7c08c0e3b75c5ead6698e25\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F6yp_uPbTpt4HXrKyJGJDSw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F108735d7b7